Package: geocoda
Title: Spatial Simulation of Compositional Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Andrew", "Brown", , "brown.andrewg@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Andrew G. Brown <brown.andrewg@gmail.com>
Description: Implements a workflow for geostatistical simulation of compositional 
    data using Isometric Log-Ratio (ILR) transformations. Supports defining validity 
    constraints, estimating multivariate covariance, and generating consistent spatial 
    fields that strictly honor sum constraints. While applicable to any compositional 
    data (e.g., geochemistry, vegetation classes), the primary application is spatial 
    simulation of soil texture separates (sand, silt, clay).
